headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange as a coach
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role on the coaching staff, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.

headline: Long end-of-quarter shots to count against NBA teams, not players
description: The NBA will implement a change for the 2025-26 season with unsuccessful end-of-period heaves being recorded as a missed attempt for the team, not the player.

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves
description: Kendrick Perkins reacts to Shams Charania's report on the NBA's rule change for end-of-quarter heaves, recalling Doc Rivers' stance encouraging players to take those shots.

headline: Trey Lyles signs with Real Madrid, leaves NBA after 10 years
description: Trey Lyles, a 10-year NBA veteran, signed a one-year deal Wednesday with Real Madrid, which plays in Spain and in the EuroLeague.

headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange as a coach
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role on the coaching staff, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.

headline: Long end-of-quarter shots to count against NBA teams, not players
description: The NBA will implement a change for the 2025-26 season with unsuccessful end-of-period heaves being recorded as a missed attempt for the team, not the player.

description: The EuroBasket is the top international basketball competition for European teams. Check out all-time men's and women's winners now.

headline: Trey Lyles signs with Real Madrid, leaves NBA after 10 years
description: Trey Lyles, a 10-year NBA veteran, signed a one-year deal Wednesday with Real Madrid, which plays in Spain and in the EuroLeague.

headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange as a coach
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role on the coaching staff, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.

headline: Long end-of-quarter shots to count against NBA teams, not players
description: The NBA will implement a change for the 2025-26 season with unsuccessful end-of-period heaves being recorded as a missed attempt for the team, not the player.

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves
description: Kendrick Perkins reacts to Shams Charania's report on the NBA's rule change for end-of-quarter heaves, recalling Doc Rivers' stance encouraging players to take those shots.

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves
description: Kendrick Perkins reacts to Shams Charania's report on the NBA's rule change for end-of-quarter heaves, recalling Doc Rivers' stance encouraging players to take those shots.

description: EuroBasket hits the court for the first time since 2022. We have all the news, scores and schedules as 24 teams compete for champion of Europe.

description: The EuroBasket is the top international basketball competition for European teams. Check out all-time men's and women's winners now.

headline: Trey Lyles signs with Real Madrid, leaves NBA after 10 years
description: Trey Lyles, a 10-year NBA veteran, signed a one-year deal Wednesday with Real Madrid, which plays in Spain and in the EuroLeague.

headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange as a coach
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role on the coaching staff, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.

headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange as a coach
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role on the coaching staff, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.

headline: Long end-of-quarter shots to count against NBA teams, not players
description: The NBA will implement a change for the 2025-26 season with unsuccessful end-of-period heaves being recorded as a missed attempt for the team, not the player.

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves
description: Kendrick Perkins reacts to Shams Charania's report on the NBA's rule change for end-of-quarter heaves, recalling Doc Rivers' stance encouraging players to take those shots.

description: EuroBasket hits the court for the first time since 2022. We have all the news, scores and schedules as 24 teams compete for champion of Europe.

headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role with the franchise, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.

headline: Long end-of-quarter shots to count against NBA teams, not players
description: The NBA will implement a change for the 2025-26 season with unsuccessful end-of-period heaves being recorded as a missed attempt for the team, not the player.

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves
description: Kendrick Perkins reacts to Shams Charania's report on the NBA's rule change for end-of-quarter heaves, recalling Doc Rivers' stance encouraging players to take those shots.

description: EuroBasket hits the court for the first time since 2022. We have all the news, scores and schedules as 24 teams compete for champion of Europe.

headline: Long end-of-quarter shots to count against NBA teams, not players
description: The NBA will implement a change for the 2025-26 season with unsuccessful end-of-period heaves being recorded as a missed attempt for the team, not the player.

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves

headline: Perk reacts to NBA rule change for end-of-quarter heaves
description: Kendrick Perkins reacts to Shams Charania's report on the NBA's rule change for end-of-quarter heaves, recalling Doc Rivers' stance encouraging players to take those shots.

headline: EuroBasket 2025: Scores, schedules, teams, news and updates
description: EuroBasket hits the court for the first time since 2022. We have all the news, scores and schedules as 24 teams compete for champion of Europe.

headline: Who has won EuroBasket? Men's and women's champions by year
description: The EuroBasket is the top international basketball competition for European teams. Check out all-time men's and women's winners now.

headline: Trey Lyles signs with Real Madrid, leaves NBA after 10 years
description: Trey Lyles, a 10-year NBA veteran, signed a one-year deal Wednesday with Real Madrid, which plays in Spain and in the EuroLeague.

headline: Sources: Knicks to hire Saint Joseph's Billy Lange
description: Saint Joseph's head coach, Billy Lange, is expected to be hired by the Knicks for a role with the franchise, sources told ESPN on Wednesday.
